org.joda.primitives.list.impl

Class ArrayBooleanList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.joda.primitives.collection.impl.AbstractPrimitiveCollectable<Boolean>
      • org.joda.primitives.collection.impl.AbstractBooleanCollection
        • org.joda.primitives.list.impl.AbstractBooleanList
          • org.joda.primitives.list.impl.ArrayBooleanList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Iterable<Boolean>, Collection<Boolean>, List<Boolean>, BooleanCollection, PrimitiveCollection<Boolean>, BooleanIterable, BooleanList, PrimitiveList<Boolean>, PrimitiveCollectable<Boolean>

    public class ArrayBooleanList
extends AbstractBooleanList
implements Cloneable
    Array based implementation of BooleanList for primitive int elements.

    This class implements List allowing seamless integration with other APIs.

    Add, Remove, Set and Clear are supported.

    Since:
    1.0
